            <h2 class="memberLink col-md-9" id="member-link-747731fb-0a30-4a2a-b7c2-0bd3fadb0efd">
                Sir S. Reed
            </h2>
        </div>
            <div class="col-md-3 hidden-sm hidden-xs right-column ">
            <a href="#contribution-747731fb-0a30-4a2a-b7c2-0bd3fadb0efd" rel="popover" class="link-to-contribution link-text" title="Share this contribution" data-placement="top"
